languages.text: "Нааки Эрэбис умерла в миг, когда осознала, что Неумирающий желает ее к себе. Тело ее вырвали из смерти, но... То, что было Нааки, ныне мертво".
"Naaki Erebis died the moment she realised the Undying One wanted her to come to Him. Her body was wrested away from death, but... That which was once Naaki is now dead."

languages.text: « Naaki Erebis est morte à l'instant où elle a compris que l'Immortel l'appelait à Ses côtés. Son enveloppe charnelle a peut-être échappé à la mort, mais... celle qui se faisait autrefois appeler ainsi n'est plus de ce monde. »
languages.original_text: "Naaki Erebis died the moment she realised the Undying One wanted her to come to Him. Her body was wrested away from death, but... That which was once Naaki is now dead."

languages.text: «Naaki Erebis murió en el preciso instante en que supo que el Inmortal la quería a Su lado. Su cuerpo fue despojado de la muerte, pero... La que una vez fue Naaki ya no existe».
languages.original_text: "Naaki Erebis died the moment she realised the Undying One wanted her to come to Him. Her body was wrested away from death, but... That which was once Naaki is now dead."

languages.text: 「ナアキ・エレビスは、不死の者が側にくることを望んでいると気づいた瞬間に死にました。彼女の肉体は死から引き戻されたが…かつてナアキだったものはもう死んでいます」
languages.original_text: "Naaki Erebis died the moment she realised the Undying One wanted her to come to Him. Her body was wrested away from death, but... That which was once Naaki is now dead."

traits.speaker: KibellahCompanion

languages.text: “当拿基·伊雷比斯意识到不死之神想见她的时候，她便已经死了。尽管她的肉体被人从死亡线上拖了回来，不过……拿基已经不在了。”

languages.text: "Naaki Erebis ist in dem Augenblick gestorben, in dem sie erkannt hat, dass der Todlose sie zu sich rufen will. Ihr Körper wurde dem Tod entrissen, doch ... Das, was einst Naaki war, ist nun tot."
